{"word":"G1389 - δολόω - dolóō - dol-o'-o - Handle deceitfully","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δολόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dolóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dol-o'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Handle deceitfully</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தந்திரமாய் நட"},{"paragraph":"1. to ensnare"},{"paragraph":"2. to corrupt"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1388 - δόλος - dólos - dol'-os/1388\">G1388</a>; to <i>ensnare</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>adulterate:</i> - handle deceitfully.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}